clinical_study.brief_title: A SHR-1210 BE Study on Healthy Subjects
clinical_study.official_title: A Bioequivalence Study of SHR-1210 in Healthy Subjects

brief_summary.textblock: The purpose of this study is to assess the bioequivalence of SHR-1210 before and after process changes.

study_design_info.intervention_model_description: This study is divided into two parts: pre-test and formal test. Each experiment will have two independent cohorts of subjects who will receive the treatment(SHR-1210 before process changes and SHR-1210 after process changes，respectively), and each cohort will be followed by 192 hours of blood sampling for pharmacokinetic assessments, with safety and tolerability.

primary_outcome.measure: Pre-test: Incidence and severity of AE/SAE/AESI (rated based on CTCAE v5.0)
Formal Test: Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: AUC0-inf
primary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

primary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: the geometric mean ration
primary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

primary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: 90% confidence interval (90% CI) of AUC0-inf
primary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Pre-test: Inter-individual coefficient of variation (CV) of the AUC0-inf of SHR-1210
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Other Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: Cmax
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Other Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: AUC0-t
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Other Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: Tmax
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Other Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: t1/2
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Other Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: CL
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Other Pharmacokinetics parameters of SHR-1210 before and after process changes in the fed state: Vss
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on pre-dose, 0.25-192 hours post-dose sampling times on Day 1 ~ Day 4 and Day 6 ~ Day 9

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: The incidence of anti-drug antibody (ADA) and neutralizing antibody (Nab) for SHR-1210
secondary_outcome.time_frame: Based on sampling times pre-dose on Day1, post-dose on Day 9 and Day 16

secondary_outcome.measure: Formal Test: Incidence and severity of adverse events (rated based on CTCAE 5.0）

intervention.description: Subjects will receive treatment SHR-1210 before process changes 20 mg
Subjects will receive treatment SHR-1210 after process changes 20 mg
